text: Mikko Keskinarkaus (born 29 June 1979) is a Finnish skier. He competed in the Nordic combined event at the 2002 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1979 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish male Nordic combined skiers Category:Olympic Nordic combined skiers of Finland Category:Nordic combined skiers at the 2002 Winter Olympics Category:People from Rovaniemi
